    "name": "死深 Die Deep",
    "steam_appid": 3211560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>当一切希望都被深渊吞噬，只剩下「<strong>战斗</strong>」能证明存在。</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于此游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《死深 Die Deep》是一款聚焦纯粹敌我对峙的动作游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有地图探索、解谜或冗余要素，唯一的核心，就是「战斗」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细观察敌人的动作，捕捉破绽、制定战略并精准出击，一次鲁莽的进攻或贪刀，就足以换来致命的失败。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操控拥有各自目标与特色的角色，在不断的激战中追寻那股能改写命运的神秘之力，进入深渊，直面死亡。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>纯粹敌我对峙的战斗体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏战斗强调专注观察敌人的动作，抓住每一个行动的契机。谨慎制定战略并精准出击，随意攻击或贪刀都可能导致致命后果。但这并不意味着角色动作缓慢笨拙，他们拥有敏捷的身手和强大的技能，让你在冷静应战中发挥淋漓尽致。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/7a25744062afacfb8c8537f3c9ad14b3.poster.avif?t=1766210470\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/7a25744062afacfb8c8537f3c9ad14b3.webm?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/7a25744062afacfb8c8537f3c9ad14b3.mp4?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>善长使用盾牌作战的 独眼战士-格尔</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>风格特异的操作角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擅长完美格挡的独眼战士，或是手持双刃的凌厉猫贼，每位角色都有截然不同的战斗风格。深入挖掘他们的特性，发挥每位角色的优势，找到属于你的制胜之道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/984389ce33e2c3fb8c81e716bb64dd41.poster.avif?t=1766210470\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/984389ce33e2c3fb8c81e716bb64dd41.webm?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/984389ce33e2c3fb8c81e716bb64dd41.mp4?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>如同暴风雨般快速输出的 双刃盗贼-赛塔</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>紧凑刺激的连续战场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着地形自动变化，战斗将持续不断袭来。你必须抓住每一丝喘息的机会来恢复，突破一场又一场的挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/b259c3b59750737c2f7f0a22391d48b6.poster.avif?t=1766210470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/b259c3b59750737c2f7f0a22391d48b6.webm?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/b259c3b59750737c2f7f0a22391d48b6.mp4?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>紧凑的战斗中别忘了回血</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>构筑多变的战斗风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透过胜利获得灵魂能量，不断成长。搭配多样化的护符与技能，打造自己的专属战斗风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/655002cbee7751db523f1963aeda4b3b.poster.avif?t=1766210470\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/655002cbee7751db523f1963aeda4b3b.webm?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211560/extras/655002cbee7751db523f1963aeda4b3b.mp4?t=1766210470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>利用魂符打造适合自己的战斗方式</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
